        <!-- Work & Travel -->
        <h1 class="gridMiniHeadline alignCenter colorPrimary">Work & Travel</h1>
        <div class="gridOpportunity">
            <!-- DiscoverEU -->
            <img class="opportunityImage" src="images/opportunities/discover-eu.png" alt="Backpacking Woman" />
            <a href="https://youth.europa.eu/discovereu_en" class="opportunityName" target="_blank">
                DiscoverEU
            </a>
            <p class="colorWhite">
                Would you like to spend a month travelling around Europe on the train? DiscoverEU is a programme funded by Erasmus+ for 18-year-old residents of
                the EU Member States whose desire is to see the world.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="gridOpportunity">
            <!-- AuPair -->
            <img class="opportunityImage" src="images/opportunities/aupair.png" alt="Woman with Children" />
            <a href="https://www.aupairworld.com/en" class="opportunityName" target="_blank">
                AuPair
            </a>
            <p class="colorWhite">
                Do you love kids, and do kids love you? Being an AuPair allows You to get to know other cultures, see the world and work in childcare while
                living abroad with a host family.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="gridOpportunity">
            <!-- Workaway -->
            <img class="opportunityImage" src="images/opportunities/workaway.png" alt="Group of People" />
            <a href="https://www.workaway.info" class="opportunityName" target="_blank">
                Workaway
            </a>
            <p class="colorWhite">
                Travelling, working and living in someone's place — Workaway is all about that. The programme allows you to go abroad and help families or
                individuals with their own (home) projects, and, in exchange, they will cover your needs.
            </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Volunteer & Intern -->
        <h1 class="gridMiniHeadline alignCenter colorPrimary">Volunteer & Intern</h1>
        <div class="gridOpportunity">
            <!-- The Hub -->
            <img class="opportunityImage" src="images/opportunities/the-hub.png" alt="Woman with a Camera" />
            <a href="https://thehub.io" class="opportunityName" target="_blank">
                The Hub
            </a>
            <p class="colorWhite">
                The Hub is a platform for all Creative Individuals who live up in the North and constantly look for opportunities. It is a place that helps you
                make your first steps in start-ups and small businesses and get involved in various creative projects — for all who would like to gain work
                experience.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="gridOpportunity">
            <!-- European Solidarity Corps (ESC) -->
            <img class="opportunityImage" src="images/opportunities/esc.png" alt="Three Volunteers" />
            <a href="https://youth.europa.eu/solidarity_en" class="opportunityName" target="_blank">
                European Solidarity Corps (ESC)
            </a>
            <p class="colorWhite">
                ESC is a funded programme for everyone who wishes to contribute and make impactful change. You will join a team of internationals abroad or in
                your home country and become part of a long-term or short-term volunteering project.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="gridOpportunity">
            <!-- EURES -->
            <img class="opportunityImage" src="images/opportunities/eures.png" alt="Woman in Suit with Blue Eyes" />
            <a href="https://ec.europa.eu/eures/portal/jv-se/home?pageCode=find_a_job" class="opportunityName" target="_blank">
                EURES
            </a>
            <p class="colorWhite">
                Would you like to find a job, paid traineeship and internships in Europe? Create an account on EURES and fill out your CV. You can browse
                thousands of unique job offers and apply for opportunities in various European countries.
            </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Study Abroad -->
        <h1 class="gridMiniHeadline alignCenter colorPrimary">Study Abroad</h1>
        <div class="gridOpportunity">
            <!-- EF Education First  -->
            <img class="opportunityImage" src="images/opportunities/education-first.png" alt="Woman Reading a Book" />
            <a href="https://www.ef.com/wwen/" class="opportunityName" target="_blank">
                EF Education First
            </a>
            <p class="colorWhite">
                How about learning a language in another country, getting to know the culture and fully immersing in another environment? EF is a programme for
                all those who are willing to study a foreign language abroad and have an educational journey in their life.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="gridOpportunity">
            <!-- ESL Languages  -->
            <img class="opportunityImage" src="images/opportunities/esl-languages.png" alt="Woman Reading in a Coffee Shop" />
            <a href="https://www.esl-languages.com/en" class="opportunityName" target="_blank">
                ESL Languages
            </a>
            <p class="colorWhite">
                ESL allows you to learn over 15 languages in various parts of the world, including Europe, North and South America and Asia. As a student, you
                receive the highest quality of education and interact with natives daily.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="gridOpportunity">
            <!-- Future Leaders Exchange (FLEX)  -->
            <img class="opportunityImage" src="images/opportunities/flex.png" alt="Woman Reading in a Coffee Shop" />
            <a href="https://www.discoverflex.org" class="opportunityName" target="_blank">
                Future Leaders Exchange (FLEX)
            </a>
            <p class="colorWhite">
                Spend a year abroad in one of the high schools in the United States of America and live with a host family. FLEX is a scholarship program that
                allows students from various parts of the world to get education while living abroad.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="gridOpportunity">
            <!-- Erasmus+ Programme  -->
            <img class="opportunityImage" src="images/opportunities/erasmus-programme.png" alt="Smiling Woman" />
            <a href="https://erasmus-plus.ec.europa.eu" class="opportunityName" target="_blank">
                Erasmus+ Programme
            </a>
            <p class="colorWhite">
                Study for a semester or two in another university or do your internship abroad. That is possible with Erasmus+, a programme that allows students
                to get international experience while pursuing their higher education.
            </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Learn New Skills -->
        <h1 class="gridMiniHeadline alignCenter colorPrimary">Learn New Skills</h1>
        <div class="gridOpportunity">
            <!-- European Bartender School (EBS) -->
            <img class="opportunityImage" src="images/opportunities/european-bartender-school.png" alt="Man Mixing Drinks" />
            <a href="https://www.barschool.net" class="opportunityName" target="_blank">
                European Bartender School (EBS)
            </a>
            <p class="colorWhite">
                Mojito, Aperol Spritz, Moscow Moule? These names will not feel foreign to you! EBS allows you to undertake a four-week training in many world
                locations and different languages and, on top of that, become a classified Bartender.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="gridOpportunity">
            <!-- SCA Education -->
            <img class="opportunityImage" src="images/opportunities/sca-education.png" alt="Barista Making Coffee" />
            <a href="https://education.sca.coffee" class="opportunityName" target="_blank">
                SCA Education
            </a>
            <p class="colorWhite">
                Would you like to learn everything about coffee? With SCA (Specialty Coffee Association), you can become a qualified Barista in just a couple of
                weeks. Your study is divided into modules, ranging from Skills, Brewing, Green Coffee to Roasting and Sensory Skills.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="gridOpportunity">
            <!-- CAFA Wine School -->
            <img class="opportunityImage" src="images/opportunities/cafa-wine-school.png" alt="Barista Making Coffee" />
            <a href="https://www.cafawine.com" class="opportunityName" target="_blank">
                CAFA Wine School
            </a>
            <p class="colorWhite">
                Become a professional Sommelier Wine Consultant and learn all the things about wine. You will spend over 500h in theoretical training and an
                extra 280h in an internship. In over 21 weeks, you will get the best quality of knowledge and skills — and all of that, in Bordeaux.
            </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Code & Design -->
        <h1 class="gridMiniHeadline alignCenter colorPrimary">Code & Design</h1>
        <div class="gridOpportunity">
            <!-- Codecademy -->
            <img class="opportunityImage" src="images/opportunities/codecademy.png" alt="Redhead Woman Coding" />
            <a href="https://www.codecademy.com" class="opportunityName" target="_blank">
                Codecademy
            </a>
            <p class="colorWhite">
                Have you ever wanted to learn how to code? With Codecademy, you can do that! They offer online courses about programming, data analysis,
                computer science, front-end engineering and many more. That's everything you need to become a Full Stack Developer.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="gridOpportunity">
            <!-- Harvard Programming Courses -->
            <img class="opportunityImage" src="images/opportunities/harvard-programming-courses.png" alt="Guy Programming" />
            <a href="https://pll.harvard.edu/subject/programming" class="opportunityName" target="_blank">
                Harvard Programming Courses
            </a>
            <p class="colorWhite">
                Improve your programming skills and knowledge with Harvard Programming Courses. Courses are designed by professionals from Harvard University
                and are available online. They take about 6–12 weeks to complete at your own pace, also for beginners.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="gridOpportunity">
            <!-- Interaction Design Foundation -->
            <img class="opportunityImage" src="images/opportunities/interaction-design-foundation.png" alt="Boy Working on the Computer" />
            <a href="https://www.interaction-design.org" class="opportunityName" target="_blank">
                Interaction Design Foundation
            </a>
            <p class="colorWhite">
                Learn about UX Design, Design Thinking, Usability and Research with Interaction Design Foundation. You can enrol in various courses, accredited
                by professionals, or join shorter classes on the topics that matter to you.
            </p>
